# 25 - Dependency Auditor
# Analyze project dependencies

NAME dep-audit
INPUT manifest_file
INPUT ecosystem DEFAULT "auto-detect"

GOAL parse "Read $manifest_file. Identify all dependencies, versions, and $ecosystem if auto-detect."
GOAL analyze "For each dependency: check for outdated versions, known vulnerabilities, and maintenance status."
GOAL recommend "Recommend: updates, replacements for unmaintained packages, and removal of unused deps."
GOAL report "Generate a dependency health report with action items sorted by priority."

RUN audit USING parse, analyze, recommend, report
